{"id": "2290", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2290", "title": "Ben's Raincoat", "text": " is an &lt;a href=\"Items\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2, added in the \"&lt;a href=\"Survivors%20of%20the%20Void\"&gt;Survivors of the Void&lt;/a&gt;\" update.\nIf the holder has any stacks of this item, most debuffs they would receive are completely negated. When this happens, a visual effect of a raincoat will be briefly displayed over the &lt;a href=\"Survivors\"&gt;Survivor&lt;/a&gt; and the item will go on a 5 second internal cooldown, represented by the debuff. Negating a debuff also gives the holder 10% &lt;a href=\"Health%23Barrier\"&gt;barrier&lt;/a&gt;. After the cooldown is over, the buff will be replaced with the buff, indicating debuffs can be negated again.\nThe holder can negate 1 (\"+1 per stack\") debuff before Ben's Raincoat goes on cooldown."}
{"id": "2294", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2294", "title": "Benthic Bloom", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Items%23Void\"&gt;void item&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2, added in the \"&lt;a href=\"Survivors%20of%20the%20Void\"&gt;Survivors of the Void&lt;/a&gt;\" expansion, and the corruption of the . \nAt the start of each stage, the item selects 3 (\"+3 per stack\") random Common or items in the holder's inventory. Each \"stack\" of a selected item randomly transforms into an equal-sized stack of a random item of the next higher rarity (for example, a stack of 4 would transform into 4 of a random green item). "}
