{"id": "2291", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2291", "title": "Eulogy Zero", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Items%23Lunar\"&gt;lunar item&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2, added in the \"&lt;a href=\"Survivors%20of%20the%20Void\"&gt;Survivors of the Void&lt;/a&gt;\" expansion. \nWhen entering a new stage, there is a 5% (\"+5% per stack\") chance for each item generated in the stage to be replaced with a random lunar item instead. This affects items in &lt;a href=\"Chests\"&gt;Chests&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"3D%20Printers\"&gt;3D Printers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Void%20Cradle\"&gt;Void Cradle&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Void%20Potential\"&gt;Void Potential Orbs&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rusted%20Key\"&gt;Rusted&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=\"Encrusted%20Key\"&gt;Encrusted&lt;/a&gt; Lockboxes, the &lt;a href=\"Teleporter%23Drops\"&gt;Teleporter reward&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=\"Bazaar%20Between%20Time%23Cauldrons\"&gt;Cauldrons&lt;/a&gt; in the . It also affects any item dropped while the is enabled, and the item dropped when using the . However, it does \"not\" affect &lt;a href=\"Items%23Elite%20Equipment\"&gt;Elite equipment&lt;/a&gt; drops.\nEulogy Zero also affects items given to monsters. This applies to the items spawn with, the items given to monsters from the , and the items monsters gain in the and &lt;a href=\"Simulacrum\"&gt;Simulacrum&lt;/a&gt;."}
