{"id": "2292", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2292", "title": "Light Flux Pauldron", "text": "The is an &lt;a href=\"Items%23Lunar\"&gt;lunar item&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2, added in the \"&lt;a href=\"Survivors%20of%20the%20Void\"&gt;Survivors of the Void&lt;/a&gt;\" expansion. \nAfter all other cooldown reduction and &lt;a href=\"Damage\"&gt;attack speed&lt;/a&gt; modifiers are applied to the holder, this item reduces \"both\" their final attack speed and final cooldowns. Cooldowns are reduced by 50% (\"-50% per stack\"), while attack speed is multiplied by codice_1.\nMath.\nSkills' new cooldowns are determined by the formula codice_2. Note that the minimum cooldown for most skills is 0.5 seconds.\nThe holder's final attack speed, however, is determined differently, with the formula codice_3."}
{"id": "432", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=432", "title": "Little Disciple", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Items%23Boss\"&gt;boss item&lt;/a&gt; introduced in the \"&lt;a href=\"Early%20Access%20Scorched%20Acres%20Content%20Update\"&gt;Scorched Acres Update&lt;/a&gt;\", dropped by the . \nWhile the holder is sprinting, they periodically shoot homing wisps at enemies, dealing 300% (\"+300% per stack\") damage per wisp. The speed at which the wisps are fired increases as movement speed increases.\nThe wisps have a range of 40m and a &lt;a href=\"Proc%20Coefficient\"&gt;proc coefficient&lt;/a&gt; of 1.0.\nMath.\n While the in-game description stating the initial rate of 1.6 seconds would be correct for a speed of 7m/s, the calculation uses your sprinting speed to determine the rate of fire. Each &lt;a href=\"Survivors\"&gt;Survivor&lt;/a&gt; has a sprinting speed of 10.15m/s (except for who has 11.6m/s), so the initial rate is one wisp every 1.15 seconds (1.01 seconds for Heretic).\nThe time in seconds between each fired wisp is determined by the formula codice_1"}
{"id": "433", "revid": "24513582", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=433", "title": "Loader", "text": "The is a playable &lt;a href=\"Survivors\"&gt;character&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2.\nAn incredibly mobile and heavy cargo loader, the Loader is capable of delivering some of the hardest-hitting attacks in the game. When utilizing velocity to her advantage, she is able to topple many powerful monsters in just a single punch. \nCompleting the &lt;a href=\"Guidance%20Offline\"&gt;Guidance Offline&lt;/a&gt; challenge will unlock Loader as a playable survivor. \nBehaviors.\n\"For an explanation of how these behaviors are implemented read about &lt;a href=\"Enemy%20AI\"&gt;Enemy AI&lt;/a&gt;. This section only applies when the character is controlled by AI.\""}
