{"id": "468", "revid": "55395716", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=468", "title": "N'kuhana's Retort", "text": "N'kuhana's Retort is an &lt;a href=\"Items%23Elite%20Equipment\"&gt;Elite equipment&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2. It can only be found as a rare drop from a &lt;a href=\"Monsters%23Malachite\"&gt;Elite&lt;/a&gt;. The drop chance is 1/4000 from each Malachite Elite, but this chance is affected by and .\nA player equipped with N'kuhana's Retort gains the power of a Malachite Elite; their attacks inflict the debuff for 8 seconds, and they will periodically release 3-4 spiked balls. On impact, the balls create a small explosion for 100% damage and sprout spike pits that deal 100% contact damage. Additionally, when the equipped player dies, a will spawn and shoot at nearby &lt;a href=\"monsters\"&gt;monsters&lt;/a&gt;, but even with this effect is of limited usefulness.\nAlthough N'kuhana's Retort is held in the equipment slot, it works passively and cannot be activated. Equipment cooldown reduction and additional equipment charges from do not affect its behavior."}
