{"id": "1394", "revid": "24513582", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1394", "title": "Parent", "text": "The is a ogre-like, sprite/spirit &lt;a href=\"Monsters\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt; added in the \"Artifacts\" Update, and is part of the monster family.\nSkills and Behavior.\nThe Parent is a monster native to Sky Meadow. While unprovoked, it slowly lumbers around along with its fellow monsters. Upon death, it will stop in place and fall forward, disintegrating into ash.\nPrimary: Seismic Smash.\nThe Parent attacks by slamming the ground with its two fists, dealing 400% damage with a &lt;a href=\"Proc%20Coefficient\"&gt;proc coefficient&lt;/a&gt; of 1.0 in a radius of 10m with &lt;a href=\"Damage%23Damage%20Falloff\"&gt;linear falloff&lt;/a&gt;. This can also knock players back depending on their positioning from the center of the blast.\nThis skill has a cooldown of 2 seconds. The animation duration is 3 seconds, which scales with &lt;a href=\"Damage%23Attack%20Speed\"&gt;attack speed&lt;/a&gt;.\nIf the Parent is airborne this skill cannot be used.\nUtility: Teleport.\nThe Parent can teleport to instantly travel a moderate distance, similarly to. However, unlike Imps, a Parent only teleports once it has spotted a player, and the Parent can't store multiple charges. The blink look-ahead distance is 30m. \nThis skill has a cooldown of 4 seconds."}
