{"id": "2408", "revid": "41355612", "url": "https://riskofrain2.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2408", "title": "Remote Caffeinator", "text": "The is an &lt;a href=\"Items%23Equipment\"&gt;equipment&lt;/a&gt; in Risk of Rain 2, added in the \"&lt;a href=\"Survivors%20of%20the%20Void\"&gt;Survivors of the Void&lt;/a&gt;\" expansion.\nWhen activated, after 5 seconds an Eclipse Zero Vending Machine crashes down, dealing 2000% damage with a &lt;a href=\"Proc%20Coefficient\"&gt;proc coefficient&lt;/a&gt; of 1.0 in a 16m radius with &lt;a href=\"Damage%23Damage%20Falloff\"&gt;sweet spot&lt;/a&gt; falloff. The vending machine can then be interacted with up to 12 times for a base cost of 5 &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt; each time (scaling with &lt;a href=\"Difficulty%23Effect%20on%20money%20costs\"&gt;difficulty&lt;/a&gt;), which dispenses up to 3 cans of soda within 25m at a time depending on how many allies are near. These cans gravitate towards the player or their allies when they get close, each healing 25% of the collector's maximum HP."}
